    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell acts as the <i>deeper slumber</i> spell, but only affects one creature of 10 Hit Dice or fewer. In addition, a creature affected by this spell awakens with no knowledge of the events that led to the spell's casting. The target loses all memory from the 5 minutes prior to falling asleep. No effect short of a <i>miracle</i> or <i>wish</i> can restore memories lost by this spell.</p>"
